{"pageProps":{"data":"<h5>delete</h5>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\">delete from <span class=\"dust\">main</span> where <span class=\"dust\">...</span> ;</span>\n</code>\n<h6>删除指定列的长度</h6>\n<p>使用 limit 来指定删除的数量（建议使用 order by 进行排序）：</p>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\">delete from <span class=\"dust\">main</span></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">order by <span class=\"dust\">...</span></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">limit <span class=\"dust\">length</span> ;</span>\n</code>","pageTitle":"computer ✈︎✈︎ 计算机基础 ✈︎✈︎ mySQL","title":"删除数据"},"__N_SSG":true}